desc: An exclusive men's clothing shop located in Dublin. Father & Son, Brian & Richard Tector specialise in quality & service. View our range of top menswear brands.

layout.text:
Where Quality Never Goes Out Of Fashion
A family run menswear business in the Swan Centre, Rathmines, Dublin. Stocking top brands such as Hugo Boss, GANT, Meyer, Bugatti and many more.
Visit us in store or shop online with free delivery over €70.
